headline: O’Reilly to Host Second AI Codecon on Coding for the Agentic World
summary: BOSTON, August 20, 2025--O’Reilly, the premier learning platform for technology professionals, today announced the second virtual conference in the AI Codecon series. Coding for the Agentic World will take place on Tuesday, September 9, 2025, from 11:00am to 3:00pm ET, and is free for all attendees.
